               <p>I was alarmed of the robbery, I went to the door, I could not see any person, I turned back to the window to see the state of it; I had not been there more than a minute before a mob of people came back with the prisoner, in custody of an officer and a runner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17911026-41-person442">
