                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am one of the patrols, I took the prisoner with the ribbon, he was walking fast.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to by a mark, being faded and spotted with flies.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I had been on some business for my father and mother, and they took me; the man run by me, and had liked to have knocked me down, and that good man picked the ribbon off the ground.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
